### Welcome on the Lausanne Ruby Brigade page

Feel free to join our [group](https://groups.google.com/d/forum/lausannerb) or follow us on [twitter](https://twitter.com/#!/lausannerb) to get in touch about the first meeting of the Lausanne Ruby Brigade. This page will be updated soon with more information.
